metadata.name: $100k pfp
metadata.description:
$100k pfp is in response to the absolute shit storm surrounding @Yieldasaurus tweet:

"If you are rocking a PFP under $100k please don't @ me or share your opinion on my wall..."

This tweet led to the 100k pfp meme storm. One for which i very much enjoyed. The tweet was later deleted forever BUT this nft is a memory of that special day.

The $100k is in done in comic sans so it's value is probably worth $1,000,000
